==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Egesta
<hw>E*ges"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL., neut.
pl. from p. p. of L. <ets>egere</ets>. See <er>Egest</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>That which is egested or thrown off from the
body by the various excretory channels; excrements; -- opposed to
<contr>ingesta</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Egestion</ent>⟦br⟧
